definitions.definition: ( astronomy ) A constellation of the zodiac supposedly shaped like a bull and containing the star Aldebaran .
( astrology ) The zodiac sign for the bull , ruled by Venus and covering April 21 - May 21 ( tropical astrology ) or May 16 - June 15 ( sidereal astrology ).

main_definition: ( astronomy ) A constellation of the zodiac supposedly shaped like a bull and containing the star Aldebaran .

definitions.definition: Someone with a Taurus star sign .
( automotive ) An automobile model produced by the Ford Motor Company (1986-present).
